### Register a beer
POST https://{{host}}/events/{{eventId}}/venues/herberg-jan/beers/ijbock

### Like a beer
POST https://{{host}}/events/{{eventId}}/venues/herberg-jan/beers/ijbock/likes?crawlerId=amolenk

### Dislike a beer
